<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>This is dropped off the Soothsayer Drelzak in the Temple of Droga.  There are 4 mobs in his room.  You can invis. through the entire dungeon with nothing agro'n on you.  With a good group of 4 to 6 level 36 to 40 characters one of which being an enchanter and one having a snare type spell this room is pathetically easy to break.  Have the tank target the Sooth and let the enchanter do his job.  Spawns every 19 minutes.  Soothslayer also drops the Bracer of Vajeen which shows as banded.</font></td></tr></table>
